<section class="suds-home">
  <div class="suds-home__wrap">
    <div class="suds-home__hero">
      <div>
        <p class="suds-home__eyebrow">Premium mobile detailing in Seattle</p>
        <h1>Private mobile detailing at your home or office.</h1>
        <p class="suds-home__lead">
          Suds Auto Salon is an owner-operated private mobile detailing service for busy drivers, families, pet owners,
          resale prep, and vehicle owners who want a cleaner interior, sharper exterior, and a simpler way to care for their car.
        </p>
        <div class="suds-home__actions">
          <a class="suds-home__button suds-home__button--primary" href="/pages/contact-us">Request a Quote</a>
          <a class="suds-home__button suds-home__button--secondary" href="{{ routes.collections_url }}/mobile-details">Book Your Mobile Detail</a>
          <a class="suds-home__textlink" href="sms:+14253618838">Text Photos for a Faster Quote</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="suds-home__panel" aria-label="Best first booking">
        <p class="suds-package__label">Best first booking</p>
        <h2>Signature Detail</h2>
        <p>
          The right choice for most vehicles that need the interior and exterior cleaned up without jumping
          straight into ceramic coating or paint correction.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Interior reset for dust, crumbs, grime, light stains, and glass.</li>
          <li>Exterior hand wash, wheels, tires, trim, and finish cleanup.</li>
          <li>Protection, pet hair, odor, and stain upgrades available.</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>

    <div class="suds-home__proof" aria-label="Suds Auto Salon service areas">
      <span>Seattle</span>
      <span>Bellevue</span>
      <span>Edmonds</span>
      <span>Lynnwood</span>
      <span>Everett</span>
      <span>Marysville</span>
      <span>Lake Stevens</span>
      <span>Snohomish</span>
    </div>

    <div class="suds-package-grid">
      <article class="suds-package">
        <p class="suds-package__label">Clean upkeep</p>
        <h2>Basic Detail</h2>
        <p>For vehicles already in good shape. Good for upkeep, light mess, and recurring maintenance.</p>
        <a href="/pages/basic-detail">View Basic</a>
      </article>

      <article class="suds-package suds-package--featured">
        <p class="suds-package__label">Most booked</p>
        <h2>Signature Detail</h2>
        <p>For most first-time bookings. A stronger inside-and-out clean with room for protection or problem-area add-ons.</p>
        <a href="/pages/signature-detail">View Signature</a>
      </article>

      <article class="suds-package">
        <p class="suds-package__label">Heavy reset</p>
        <h2>Elite Reset</h2>
        <p>For neglected interiors, family SUVs, pet vehicles, resale prep, and cars that need more time.</p>
        <a href="/pages/elite-detail">View Elite</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="suds-money">
  <div class="suds-money__wrap">
    <div>
      <p class="suds-home__eyebrow">Maintenance plan</p>
      <h2>Keep the car clean after the first reset.</h2>
      <p>
        After the first reset, monthly maintenance keeps the vehicle under control and gives you priority scheduling.
        Best for commuter cars, family vehicles, luxury cars, and anyone who wants a clean car without starting over every few months.
      </p>
    </div>
    <a class="suds-home__button suds-home__button--primary" href="/pages/contact-us">Ask About Maintenance</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="suds-seo">
  <div class="suds-seo__wrap">
    <h2>Mobile detailing in Seattle, Bellevue, Edmonds, Lynnwood, Everett, Marysville, Lake Stevens, and Snohomish.</h2>
    <p>
      Suds Auto Salon provides mobile car detailing, interior car detailing, full detail resets, ceramic protection,
      paint enhancement, pet hair removal, odor treatment, and maintenance detailing across Seattle and nearby Eastside and North Sound areas.
    </p>
    <div class="suds-faq">
      <article>
        <h3>Do you come to my location?</h3>
        <p>Yes. Suds Auto Salon is mobile and can detail at homes, offices, apartments, and approved service locations.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Which detail should I book?</h3>
        <p>Basic is for upkeep, Signature is best for most first bookings, and Elite Reset is for heavier interiors or resale prep.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Do photos help with quotes?</h3>
        <p>Yes. Photos help Suds spot pet hair, stains, odor issues, heavy grime, or paint concerns before recommending a package.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

